@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ayjoyo(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.exp((v1 + 0.90 - v1 + 0.62)))
    v1 = (v1 * tmp)
    tmp = wp.abs((wp.abs(v1 + 0.77) * (v0 + 0.99 / v2 + 0.08)))
    tmp = 0.35
    v2 = 0.18
    data[tid] = v0
